&ANALYZE-SUSPEND _UIB-CODE-BLOCK _CONTROL cFileExport gDialog
ON LEAVE OF cFileExport IN FRAME gDialog /* Output File */
DO:
    /* trim value */
  SELF:SCREEN-VALUE = TRIM(SELF:SCREEN-VALUE).
END.

